lign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   VS Raid?</span><hr size=1> I'm just wondering what the min level people will take on this is... I only need his stone to complete my epic... kinda given up on it now and contemplating selling the stuff that I have that I can sell to make some cash <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :/ --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/ohwell.gif ALT=":/"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
