<br>
1. Kill VS then Remains spawn.<br>
(Note: 2 and 3 may be backwards)<br>
2. Give remains Globe of Fireflies this makes Ghost spawn<br>
3. Give Ghost lvl 49 Cleric Res scroll this makes VS respawn with Stones only<br>
4. Wait 7 days for VS to respawn so you can make remains respawn<br>
<br>
Still have to kill VS just made the fight longer, unless yesterdays patch made Remains respawn every X hours after being killed untill VS respawns. Since most raids will bring someone needing the Stones Remains wont be up for another raid to come in and kill the Stone only Venril Sathir<br>
<br>
