Lilliana <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utakrawindrider.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Takra Windrider</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 69<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/3/01 9:18:09 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: no</span><hr size=1> there is a way to not kill VS at all.  Go to HS and kill VS's sister or wife and loot some crazy named thing and turn that into the remains.  No killing of the second weaker VS and you still get a stone.<br>
